name: GEN.ART Membership
description: As a member of GEN.ART you’ll be able to mint exclusive NFT (ERC-721) artwork by world-renowned artists. We’re limiting membership to 5,100. As a lifetime member, you will not only be part of a special group of collectors and artists but have an active say in the future of GEN.ART through governance tokens (ERC-20) that will be airdropped.
